---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Prop Bags" description="Golden Atlas Players prop bags for Rocky Horror nights, including audience participation props and instruction cards for $10.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <span class="badge">Prop Bags</span>
      <h1>Get ready to Time Warp.</h1>
      <p class="hero__intro">Golden Atlas Players prop bags include the classic Rocky Horror audience-participation goodies, helpful instruction cards, and everything you need to jump in without guessing what happens when. Prop bags are just $10 at the show.</p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn" href="/shows">Ask about prop bags at the show</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__figure">
      <img src="/images/prop/Prop-Bag.jpg" alt="A Golden Atlas Players prop bag ready for an audience member to use at a Rocky Horror show." />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Price</h3>
        <p class="section-copy">Prop bags are $10 each.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Includes</h3>
        <p class="section-copy">Props plus instruction cards that explain what to use and when.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Best for</h3>
        <p class="section-copy">First-timers, returning fans, and anyone who wants to participate without overthinking it.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="two-col">
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title">What’s inside?</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">The bag includes the usual Rocky Horror participation pieces, along with an instruction card that helps you follow along without guessing. It is a simple way to take part, whether you are new to the room or know the routine by heart.</p>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Bubbles</li>
        <li>Newspaper</li>
        <li>Cell phone light</li>
        <li>Rubber gloves</li>
        <li>Noisemakers</li>
        <li>Confetti</li>
        <li>Toilet paper</li>
        <li>Toast</li>
        <li>Party hat</li>
        <li>Car keys</li>
        <li>Playing cards</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="image-card">
      <img src="/images/prop/gap-prop-bag-list.jpg" alt="A prop bag list showing the items included with a Golden Atlas Players Rocky Horror bag." />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="two-col">
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title">New to Rocky Horror?</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">You do not need to know every callback or bring a suitcase full of supplies. The prop bag gives you the basics and helps you follow along, whether it is your first time or your fiftieth.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <h3>Helpful without being complicated</h3>
      <p class="section-copy">Prop bags make participation feel easy. They help people jump in without wondering what to bring, what to do, or when to use it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="two-col">
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Learn the Time Warp</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">The prop bag includes a Time Warp card so you can follow along when the room starts moving. It is a nice little guide for first-timers and a fun refresher for regulars.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-card">
      <img src="/images/prop/Time-Warp-card.jpg" alt="A Time Warp instruction card included with the Golden Atlas Players prop bag." />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Respect the theatre, respect each other</h2>
    <p class="section-copy">Have fun. Do not throw things at people. Follow cast and theatre guidance, keep aisles and walkways safe, and help new people feel welcome.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="gallery-grid">
    <div class="image-card">
      <img src="/images/prop/Denton-Paper.jpg" alt="A playful prop bag reference card with a handmade feel that fits the Rocky Horror mood." />
    </div>
    <div class="image-card">
      <img src="/images/prop/Prop-Bag.jpg" alt="A Golden Atlas Players prop bag ready for audience use at the theatre." />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 540px;
  }

  .hero__figure img {
    width: min(420px, 100%);
    border-radius: 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(213, 180, 111, 0.24);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
  }

  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .image-card {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(213, 180, 111, 0.24);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .image-card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .card-grid,
    .two-col,
    .gallery-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
